# Normalize line endings: store as LF, check out as LF on every platform.
# Without this, Git's default core.autocrlf=true on Windows rewrites files to
# CRLF on checkout, which breaks byte-exact fixture tests (e.g. theme.test.ts)
# and Biome's format check on non-JS files.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files: never touch.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ico binary
